      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six architecture. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the powerband. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. This unit features essential preventative mechanical work, including a reinforced rear subframe and serviced rod bearings, maintaining the structural integrity required for spirited driving. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, while the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback synonymous with this chassis. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical synchronization is superb.",
